name: The Bride of Sun
description:
I grew up in a city called Valencia (the bride of the sun says a song) whose department is "Carabobo" in English "Sillyface" because according to legend the Indians of this region had too friendly faces.

My city is in the center of the country, land of the eternal summer, where life is very frenetic, people always go fast everywhere, take pictures in the street can be a challenge, this time I took pictures of Mirta while my cousin watched that nobody come to rob us, I remember that he said; someone is looking at us, so we took some more photos and we left there for prevent.

For me that is power, standing up to the apparent external forces and daring to create, transform the fear. 

Mirta Marquez | Carabobo | 2016
